A '''deckhead''' is the underside of a [[Deck (ship)|deck]] in a [[ship]]. It bears the same relationship to a [[Compartment (ship)|compartment]] on the deck below as does the ceiling to the room of a [[house]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Deckhead|url=http://oxforddictionaries.com/definition/english/deckhead|publisher=Oxford Dictionaries|accessdate=15 November 2012}}</ref> 

