{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2013}} {{Infobox writer <!-- for more information see [[:Template:Infobox writer/doc]] --> | name = V. M. Devadas | image = Devadas V.M Malayalam Novelist from Kerala.jpg| | native_name = വി.എം ദേവദാസ് | birth_date = March, 1981 | birth_place = [[Wadakkancherry]], [[Thrissur]], [[Kerala]] | occupation = Novelist, [[short story writer]] | language = [[Malayalam]] | nationality = Indian | genre = Novel, short story, essays | subject = Social aspects | notableworks = Pannivetta, Shalabhajeevitham | website = [http://devadasvm.blogspot.com Official blog] }}
'''V. M. Devadas''' (born March 1981) is a [[Malayalam]] [[novelist]], [[short-story]] writer and [[screenwriter]] from [[Wadakkancherry]], [[Kerala]], [[India]]. He is presently working in an IT company in Chennai.
